{"tid":633503,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"收工返到屋企 發現自己抽鎖匙插左係門鎖度","createTime":"2018-04-18T11:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T13:14:29.000Z","uid":98507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6cc4996e19cd0d499b988b0d6d1134ca3de510f1","tid":633503,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T11:18:38.000Z","msg":"說話我搭緊lift嗰時已經摷緊鎖匙 但搵極都搵唔到<br />\n咁咪行去屋企門口等老豆老母收工救命<br />\n點知一行埋去發現自己抽鎖匙插撚左係門鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我問係咪老母做(因為佢最後出門)<br />\n佢話冇<br />\n而且老母朝早落完樓發現唔記得帶左又返過屋企一次<br />\n佢話唔見門鎖有插過鎖匙<br />\n我老豆就最早出門同冇返過屋企 亦都唔會係佢做<br />\n屋企冇唔見野 冇比人摷過<br />\n屌喇星好撚神奇 到底發生左咩事<br />\n懷疑緊會唔會係我跌左條鎖匙係門口附近<br />\n有鄰居見到就好心幫我插落門度等我返黎有門入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e02805cfdf44cb6922cd986b42e89d125b9dd81","tid":633503,"uid":100131,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T11:20:41.000Z","msg":"話唔埋配咗spare, 等你屋企全家去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c959b2586ce656f2332afc668a0893bc4f5ce84","tid":633503,"uid":50780,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T11:21:38.000Z","msg":"打開衣櫃睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896204260763caa8cf34c1668b23c0cf213bbf56","tid":633503,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e02805cfdf44cb6922cd986b42e89d125b9dd81","tid":633503,"uid":100131,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T11:20:41.000Z","msg":"話唔埋配咗spare, 等你屋企全家去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T11:25:58.000Z","msg":"有諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能驚我換鎖所以插返係度<br />\n如果咁做目標就唔係偷野 唔通...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過點都會換鎖"},{"pid":"4af3d49e66396c32abf2f3e41ca3d13216312551","tid":633503,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid